    "The results of the proposed model for both uni-grams and bi-grams representations are displayed in Fig. 3.",
    "Overall, the LR and SVM algorithms demonstrate the best performance with an accuracy of 86.3%, precision of 87%, recall of 86%, and F-measure of 86%.",
